  <article class="about__service" id="service-shopping">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        Personal Shopping
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="service">
      If we determine that you need some new pieces to fill in the holes in your wardrobe, then shopping is the next step! This can be done with or without you, and we can shop locally, out of town, or online. These specifics can be established in your consultation, and will be tailored to suit your style, as well as your lifestyle goals. After shopping we will have a fitting to decide what works, what doesn’t, what needs to be tailored, and what will work best in your current wardrobe.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="about__service" id="service-trips">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        Group Trips
      </h4>
    </header>
    <p class="service">
      Curated shopping trips are the perfect way to celebrate birthdays, anniversaries, new motherhood, or just a great excuse to spend time with friends and family. <span class="fake__break">I currently offer trips to Atlanta, Nashville, and New York, with a couple of new exciting locations coming in 2019! Depending on your budget and desires, we can put together a day trip to Atlanta or a fully curated long weekend in New York.</span>
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="about__service" id="service-packing">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        Travel Packing
      </h4>
    </header>
    <p class="service">
      We all have difficulty packing, and most women (as well as more than a few men!) are chronic over-packers. I will help you determine the pieces that will allow for maximum versatility on any trip, and I’ll help eliminate the time and stress of packing and organizing your suitcase, so that you can focus your pre-trip time on more important things. <span class="fake__break">Whether it’s a business trip or a beach vacation, your wardrobe will be personalized according to destination, weather forecast, and any planned events on your itinerary. Your included outfits will be pictured and outlined in order to take all of the deliberation and stress out of getting dressed, and keep your attention where it matters.</span>
    </p>
  </article>

